https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Shelley_Winters

EDIT -THANK YOU for the Most Viral my Dudes!

One thing to bear in mind my dudes as you think about a reply is this...
Remember how you aren't supposed to judge people from the past by today's standards? This would be a good example of that. 
Shelly rose to fame in the old school Hollywood. You had to either sleep with the director or producer, know someone in the business or be really damn talented like she was. Most women at the time were probably never this bold except for a few. For her to do something like this, it was pretty ballsy to say the least. I posted this because I like someone who isn't afraid to remind people that she has earned the respect that she should have received from the beginning. She's not Tom Hanks but imagine someone asking Tom Hanks for his resume and a headshot. Can you imagine how insulting that would be to him? I can see him doing the same thing. You might disagree and you are entitled to do so but for me, I like her moxie.</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/Ro2DvVO</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[imflukeskywalker]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Mick Wallace on the US being a democracy</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/cIE66FO</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/F76lv9s.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/cIE66FO</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[phreakingout]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Still got the moves</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/HX5bTNa</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/8Tw3D7b.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/HX5bTNa</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[vidadobl6]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Another round of curated memes</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/DNc4iGW</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/9V0S9KW.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/QeQNRPX.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/A9ciTrr.jpg" style="