"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/8SaZdHE</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[OctopussSevenTwo]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Starfish Hitler. Yes you read that correctly.</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/RjGhfOV</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/LQu4Jo1.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Absolute madness</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/RjGhfOV</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[DontTellMeWhatToDoBawbags]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>How It's Going</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/TcyOJm2</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/ZDCVa8L.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>#politics #wtf #seriously_though_wtf</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/TcyOJm2</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[mfrybeasley]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Speaking something into existence</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/wxOiUUe</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/8dHQax3.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>(This post is more of a mental assertion on my part that i'm going to do it no matter how nervous I feel right now about it. If you'd like to stick around for the short story, welcome).

A woman that I have been great friends with these past few months has completely taken up my field of view. Literally. I see nothing and pay attention to nobody else except her, and recent signs that I have been otherwise stupid for ignoring have delayed me doing this. Until now.

An evening spent bowling with friends eventually turned into just us for a walk in the park late at night, when literally hours prior I had nearly spilled by feelings right then and there. She's smart, and im certain she knew where our conversations that night were going. But I didn't do it.

The next day, a 4th of July fireworks show with friends again. We were somewhat late, and we never regrouped with them. It was just us. Another walk through gardens, our path illuminated only by the soft lights hanging above.

It was that night when I dropped her home, that she spoke something to me in Japanese. I was surprised that she was fluent, and I had responded back in Greek "Goodnight" over text when I got home as a way of reciprocating. Apparently the Hellenic alphabet did not work on her phone, but she replied again in Japanese "I can't read it, but thank you. Goodnight".

What she sent me next, by the source of several native speakers, translated into "It was a romantic time". And if that isn't a green light, then I don't know.

But I am going to do it.</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/wxOiUUe</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[Mickey421]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>our future is safe because of people like her (IG: @sarpmeme)</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/duRahjL</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/jETquUa.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>follow https://www.instagram.com/sarpmeme for more</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/duRahjL</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[AdanEvin]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Losers</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/kOKoyAd</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/O7vpWjR.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/kOKoyAd</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[DraMoonBreaker]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Bisexual daughter of Iowa GOP state senator cuts ties with him</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/NXfp93a</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/bJqciy3.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/6bYTQkR.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/O4WHDfR.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/MSqSKFM.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/tDZVlCt.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Bisexual daughter cuts ties to her dad. He’s a GOP state senator who is “taking my rights” away / 
