iv><div><span></span></div><div>They must be lesbians. Only way to tell for sure is if the supervillain is like “I love u” and the hero goes “aww I love u too babe!” And then does nothing different.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/qGDCm0M.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>I see absolutely no reason to get this for my 7 month old</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/MJ3RVIU.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>It’s actually not inaccurate my therapist recommends this a lot</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/88m50Gh.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/lhbP6Od.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>I’m asleep by then no thank u</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/WWlbjju.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Probably several things</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/wcUzltQ.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/bRngNgI.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>They’re not wrong</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/KjP4qjZ.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>She’s in jail for like 15 life sentences but I’m proud of her (she tried to poison her husband but he didn’t drink the drink and it got put into the punch bowl at a party and a bunch of people died)</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/Bm7x6jA.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>I mean Jim and Pam are cute but I can see how they might both be like nah, Jim is like 80% of the cute</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/xJmVTfy.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>It’s easy! It’s fun! It’s free!</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/Izqrvji.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>I love every single thing about this. That thing is even my favorite weapon. Not quite as useful as the shotgun but damn is it stylish</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/B3wvm6K.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>He’s right, she’s being absurd, date hobbits everyone</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/uSZOHWA.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Keeper</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/0rfqUpK.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>God says a lot of things that nobody listens to, she is very wise</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/WcF5LER.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/46FIUAh.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>I hate my neighbors so much</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/GPYzNDC.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/xdfVRET.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>AC is what I imagine it’s like to be a serf for a really chill lord</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/7HvVqqJ.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/qIKboD7.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Mood. Personally I -am- a threat but I guess I don’t look threatening. Smh.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/Lh2QagT.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Disability Pride Month actually. Not that anyone cares.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/LdrJPSh.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/zyV74S7.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/dpJ6V7x.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/n0Z5uuh.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>IT (2022) with Beverly in butterfly clips and one of those crinkly crop tops in the flashbacks</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/eEWruKf.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/rFJTKk0.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/Cevm5eD.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/xSxzWyN.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>It’s extremely nice. I lived in Rome for the summer. And it’s not exactly WALKABLE but like on my way to the bus to school I passed everything I needed. It was amazing.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/zvz2QaP.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/OUnHhor.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>I read “hetero help” and I was like bitch they don’t know</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/8tYEV6G.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>That kids autistic. I’m taking bets. He is exactly like me as a child</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/IY2rEDu.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/xUn2SXc.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Yep. Especially when it comes to the female reproductive system. They’re just like “shrug” “can I offer you birth control pills that are super closely controlled for no reason?” “Or perhaps a mint? That will be 5,000$”</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/Hb5ckBK.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>This counts. Probably.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/wIZ3JAD.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Whoever sent this to me can’t crop for shit but they’re right</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/SDyiLHU.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Divergent evolution technically. Just like fish.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/44Bux5r.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>This is how I operate. Out of sheer spite. Every time someone posts a mean comment I do another post and mock them on it.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/5eI3piL.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Lizard tax! This is Queen Elizardbeth and I made those wings out of wire and leather scraps</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/tLGMpr0</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[kirbyvictorious]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>have a nice day...</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/4mbbj9T</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/2YDcE0z.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/4mbbj9T</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[aerrorfree]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Tired of reading the bible to figure out what happened?</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/0cwsFFR</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/sRJLigD.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><gu